# Unique Autos - Car Care Services Website

A modern, responsive, and animated multi-page website built for a premium auto service center named **Unique Autos**.  
The project is created using **pure HTML and CSS (Flexbox-based layout)** with smooth animations, 3D visual effects, and a dark red-black automotive theme.

---

## 🚗 Live Demo

🔗 Deployed Website:  
https://unique-autos.vercel.app/index.html

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This website represents a professional car care service brand offering:

- Interior & Exterior Car Cleaning  
- Foam Wash & Detailing  
- Denting & Painting  
- Engine Oil & AC Services  
- Tire & Wheel Services  
- General Vehicle Inspection  

The design focuses on a **modern automotive aesthetic** with 3D motion effects, hover animations, and a fully responsive layout.

---

## 🎨 Features

- Modern dark red-black UI theme  
- Fully responsive design 
- Smooth scroll animations  
- 3D hover and floating image effects  
- Flexbox-based layout (minimal grid usage)  
- Sticky navigation bar with blur effect  
- Animated buttons and interactive cards  
- Clean and structured multi-page design  
- Custom local fonts and images only  
- No external UI frameworks used  

